    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Also, when doing a search on the webpage (eg, on Chrome, control+f) the ESCAPE key not only closes the search dropdown but also moves the page back to top. Should just close the dropdown. That is annoying when you search to find something and you lose it because the page moves back to top.  Workaround: close search box by clicking on X.\n"
